attributes.title: Soapwalla Deodorant
attributes.description:
Created on April 20, 2011 by rlb372 on Sourcemap.org:

Soapwalla's all-natural deodorant provides all the protection of a drugstore brand, but without any of the incredibly dangerous additives found in most mainstream deodorants.
